{"type": "article", "id": 7232, "title": "Net-Zero House 环保材料建筑", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-10T07:52:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234159GQkItxbBLY8XSryF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t西雅图建筑设计公司 Dwell Development LLC 联合建筑设计师 Julian Weber 打造了一座全部采用纯天然，回收并且可再次回收材料的房子。这座房子有三层高，面积为3140 平方英尺。其外围栅栏由金属构成，外表涂有健康无害且耐久性强的涂料，而不是传统为防止水分渗入的墙纸。大阳台上采用的是谷仓木材，屋顶上有太阳能板，为整个房子提供能源。三层窗户保温性极强，而室内的热能回收通风机可以保证屋子里面的空气清新。为了保证能源消耗量最小，房子采取的是地板辐射采暖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341562IHKZQmGxXj5AbeE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234157Yl49j6fOuGx0mJFc.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234157Gtundm6ENrCPcBLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234157m1ZX4cpnC3HBiaMq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234158ir21BtpOvQhjq3cz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}